00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:47.000
So that would mean when I'm doing resampling, I would train on this,

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:49.000
estimate on this, train on this, estimate on this.

00:12:49.000 --> 00:12:55.000
You know what, I'm going to actually switch to bootstrap resamples

00:12:55.000 --> 00:13:00.000
